Package model

Class Toy

java.lang.Object
model.Toy
Direct Known Subclasses:
Animals, Board_Games, Figures, Puzzles
public abstract class Toy extends Object
The Toy class represents a toy that can be sold in a store. This is an abstract class, so it cannot be instantiated directly. Instead, subclasses of Toy must be created to represent specific types of toys.
